column2: ggplotly(ggplot(data[,list("avgsO2"=mean(so2),"avgnO2"=mean(no2)),by=c("year","month","state")],aes(x=as.factor(month),y=avgsO2,fill=as.factor(month),group=1))+geom_line(aes(x=as.factor(month),y=avgnO2))+geom_bar(stat = "identity")+facet_wrap(~as.factor(state))+labs(title = "Average So2 level in stats by months",x="Months", y = "Average So2 value",fill="months")+theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5,face = "bold",color = "black")))
